snippet.textDisplay:
Hey gorgeous. I wanna start off with saying that I am so proud of you for your coming out video! I have loved you for many years, and your giggle after saying "hello guys, it's me, nikkie, hello" always makes me smile 😊
now, I remember a video you did (I don't remember when), but you said something like "it's called tutorials for a reason but I don't really explain so much". What I would love is for you to talk about blending (especially for eyeshadow bc you are like a legend, what brushes to use for what part of the blending, styles, bring up hooded eyes and tips for us with that), maybe do's and dont's you've learned over the years! Also tips for brows (you mostly do those off camera) but when you are doing something new with them or with a new product/tool, you should to them on camera, cause girl - you have had many different brows and you always do them so well (and its kinda all about the brows now I feel)!
I wanna thank you for being you ❤, you are so funny and genuine, and REAL!
